These are my personal themes created using the EDHM-UI application

'Clarity' Thems are intended to be subtle - yet provide clear information to the Cmdr piloting the ship

*******************************************
ClarityCool (v1) - 2025-01-10

Overall light / pale blue 
Night Vision is more bluish
Green Speed / PIP / Status Indicators
Yellow stars / Green planets / Blue moons
Radar: Green friendly / Unknown Blue / Yellow Scanning you / Red Enemy / White Cargo - Materials
Yellow Weapon Aim
Green / Red Ship and Planet Landing indications
Red EZ / Orange Orbital Cruise / Grey Orbits
Mining:  Pale-blue Pulse / Green Cores

(used EliteNautica theme as starting point)
